quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  20,90,"Àti pé dájúdájú Hārūn ti sọ fún wọn ṣíwájú pé: “Ẹ̀yin ìjọ mi, wọ́n kàn fi ṣe àdánwò fun yín ni. Dájúdájú Olúwa yín ni Àjọkẹ́-ayé. Nítorí náà, ẹ tẹ̀lé mi. Kí ẹ sì tẹ̀lé àṣẹ mi.”"
  20,91,"Wọ́n wí pé: “A ò níí yé dúró sọ́dọ̀ rẹ̀ títí (Ànábì) Mūsā yóò fi padà sọ́dọ̀ wa.”"
  20,92,"(Ànábì) Mūsā sọ pé: \"Hārūn, kí ni ó kọ̀ fún ọ nígbà tí o rí wọn tí wọ́n ṣìnà"
  20,93,láti tọ̀ mí wá? Ṣé o yapa àṣẹ mi ni
  20,94,"(Ànábì Hārūn) sọ pé: “Ọmọ ìyá mi, má ṣe fi irungbọ̀n mi tàbí orí mi fà mí (mọ́ra). Dájúdájú èmi páyà pé ó máa sọ pé: 'O dá òpínyà sílẹ̀ láààrin àwọn ọmọ ’Isrọ̄’īl. O ò sì ṣọ́ ọ̀rọ̀ mi"
  20,95,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “Kí ni ọ̀rọ̀ tìrẹ ti jẹ́, Sāmiriyy?”"
  20,96,"(Sāmiriyy) wí pé: “Mo rí ohun tí wọn kò rí. Mo sì bu ẹ̀kúnwọ́ kan níbi (erùpẹ̀) ojú ẹsẹ̀ (ẹṣin) Òjíṣẹ́ (ìyẹn, mọlāika Jibrīl). Mo sì dà á sílẹ̀ (láti fi mọ ère). Báyẹn ni ẹ̀mí mi ṣe (aburú) ní ọ̀ṣọ́ fún mi.”"
  20,97,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “Nítorí náà, máa lọ. Dájúdájú (ìjìyà) rẹ nílé ayé yìí ni kí o máa wí pé, “Má fi ara kàn mí”. Àti pé dájúdájú ọjọ́ ìyà kan ń bẹ fún ọ tí Wọn kò níí gbé fò ọ́. Kí o sì wo ọlọ́hun rẹ, èyí tí o takú tì lọ́rùn, dájúdájú a máa dáná sun ún. Lẹ́yìn náà, dájúdájú a máa ku eérú rẹ̀ dànù pátápátá sínú agbami odò"
  20,98,"Ọlọ́hun yin ni Allāhu nìkan, kò sí ọlọ́hun tí ìjọ́sìn tọ́ sí àfi Òun. Ó fi ìmọ̀ gbòòrò ju gbogbo n̄ǹkan"
  20,99,"Báyẹn ni A ṣe ń sọ ìtàn fún ọ nínú àwọn ìró tí ó ti ṣíwájú. Láti ọ̀dọ̀ Wa sì ni A kúkú ti fún ọ ní ìrántí (ìyẹn, al-Ƙur’ān)"
  20,100,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá gbúnrí kúrò níbẹ̀, dájúdájú ó máa ru ẹrù ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde"
  20,101,Olùṣegbére ni wọ́n nínú (ìyà) rẹ̀. (Ẹrù ẹ̀ṣẹ̀) sì burú fún wọn láti rù ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde
  20,102,"Ní ọjọ́ tí wọ́n á fọn fèrè oníwo fún àjíǹde. A sí máa kó àwọn ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀ jọ ní ọjọ́ yẹn, ojú wọn yó sì dúdú batakun"
  20,103,"Wọn yó sì máa sọ̀rọ̀ ní jẹ́ẹ́jẹ́ láààrin ara wọn pé: \"Ẹ̀yin kò gbé ilé ayé tayọ (ọjọ́) mẹ́wàá"
  20,104,"Àwa nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ohun tí wọ́n ń wí nígbà tí ẹni-abiyì jùlọ nínú wọn wí pé: “Ẹ kò gbé ilé ayé tayọ ọjọ́ kan.”"